query:
UPDATE vocabulary_items_view
            SET 
                spelling = $2,
                disambiguation = $3,
                pronunciation = $4,
                phonetic_respelling = $5,
                audio_url = $6,
                register = $7,
                cefr_level = $8,
                definitions = $9,
                synonyms = $10,
                antonyms = $11,
                collocations = $12,
                definition_count = $13,
                example_count = $14,
                quality_score = $15,
                status = $16,
                last_modified_at = $17,
                last_modified_by = $18,
                version = $19
            WHERE item_id = $1 AND version = $20
